                  </hi>I am the prosecutor's wife. I never received this 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. from the prisoner—on the 16th of May, he told me Mrs. Fenado was out, and she would come and pay me on the Monday morning.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
